{
  "texts": [
    "Third is making online (especially outsourced) work possible through platforms (ridesharing, food delivery).",
    "Fourth is increasing worker mobility, enabling work from anywhere, any time, \"on demand.\"",
    "And fifth is empowering self-employed micro-entrepreneurs through e-commerce platforms (Etsy).",
    "Digitalization is Janus-faced, enabling efficiency and profits, on one hand, and exclusion and exploitation, on the other.",
    "It is up to humans to make morally balanced choices.These organizational features of work digitalization affect workers differently, according to education and skill levels, with repercussions on earnings."
  ]
}